item.title: Installation OpenStack CLI
item.description: On this page, you can find an explanation of how install OpenStack CLI on Linux VM in Cloud Console. Table of contents Prerequisites Install OpenStack CLI on Ubuntu VM Install OpenStack CLI on Centos VM Prerequisites In this article, we will assume that we have already created the following resources, that refer to the Project named dev1 that was created in the Organization named Test-Shop: API User, created with the following parameters and its RC file has already been loaded: Name: testCLIuser; Password: P@sword.
